Ministry of Sound Maximum Bass Nitro (2013) 

    Hip Hop, Club, Electro House, Hardstyle | Ministry Of Sound Australia Pty Ltd

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013 | 03:43:26 | 516 Mb



Start those engines and rev them high bass lovers - your favourite compilation is back! Download Maximum Bass Nitro from iTunes Revved Up, geared up and polished to perfection, Ministry of Sound brings you MAXIMUM BASS NITRO. Slicker than a wax-job and hotter than a new pair of chromes, MAXIMUM BASS NITRO is three discs of the biggest and best bass tunes which need to be turned up LOUD!

Ensuring all bases are covered, Ministry of Sound Australia have invited the three biggest artists in the bass game to mix this mammoth release - with master of club land G-Wizard driving Disc 1, two-times Platinum selling Bombs Away & Dixie bringing you Disc-2, and the almighty Toneshifterz bringing it home hard-style on Disc 3.
